1.title: Welcome to the Abbey

episode of.title: What Happens at the Abbey (TV Series 2017– )

1.plot: Legendary Hollywood nightclub and celebrity hotspot, The Abbey, employs a dynamic staff of beautiful and charismatic up-and-coming stars! On the series premiere of What Happens At The Abbey, superstars Tori Spelling and Brandi Glanville stop by, throwing newbie Marissa off her game, and temperatures flare as a rowdy staff party turns into tears.

2.title: Chicken Leg Bitch

episode of.title: What Happens at the Abbey (TV Series 2017– )

2.plot: Heidi Montag drops by The Abbey. Marissa's mom travels to L.A. to try to convince her baby to come home. Lawrence and Brandi find out if they're 'fit' to be parents. Cory and Murray's relationship reaches a breaking point.

3.title: Homie Hopper

episode of.title: What Happens at the Abbey (TV Series 2017– )

3.plot: After Kyle learns Marissa has a boyfriend back home, he sets his sights on another. Cory decides to try to work through his issues with Murray, but it doesn't last long when drama unfolds at Lawrence's charity event. Elizabeth has a meltdown and causes a scene when she feels she's been "disrespected" by Kyle.

4.title: Weasel-Eyed Little Ferret

episode of.title: What Happens at the Abbey (TV Series 2017– )

4.plot: The Abbey crew heads to Palm Springs for a photo shoot where Billy and Ashlee heat things up. Chelsea can't manage her anger towards Ashlee and Murray after Kyle instigates a rumor.

5.title: Gossip Girl Kyle

episode of.title: What Happens at the Abbey (TV Series 2017– )

5.plot: Kyle thinks his relationship with Marissa is on the right path, but Marissa pumps the brakes.

6.title: Vegas Bound

episode of.title: What Happens at the Abbey (TV Series 2017– )

6.plot: Cory and Murray decide to make a pact to keep their relationship in one piece while David reaches the end of his rope with Chelsea.

7.title: Stage Five Clinger

episode of.title: What Happens at the Abbey (TV Series 2017– )

7.plot: In the season finale, the Abbey crew's Vegas drama continues but they must first pull off a successful pop-up event before they can really let loose. While Kyle and Marissa's relationship hangs in the balance, Kim and Elizabeth's relationship implodes. Brandi finally reveals to Lawrence HER baby plan and the Chapel is finally revealed.

imdb.plot outline: E! goes behind the bar and takes an inside look at the lives of the employees of the world-famous hot spot when its new docu-series "What Happens at The Abbey". Located in the heart of Los Angeles' West Hollywood neighborhood, The Abbey, hailed as the "Best Gay Bar in the World," is an institution where labels are abandoned, inclusion is paramount and everyone, regardless of their sexuality comes to mix and mingle with celebrities. Presiding over one of the wildest nightclubs in Los Angeles, the team unapologetically embodies the open-minded mentality of The Abbey while fostering an environment of acceptance. Managed by owner David Cooley, the staff juggles delivering first-rate service to their VIP guests and celebrities while dealing with relationship drama, diverse sexuality and the pursuit of their own Hollywood dreams. It's not all work, as this outrageous and unpredictable squad somehow manages to party even harder than their celebrity patrons.
